---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import FAQSchema from "../../../components/FAQSchema.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Carpet Cleaning Montreal | Expert Home Service"
  description="Professional residential carpet and stair cleaning in Montreal. Specialists for condos and homes with our truck-mounts and portable extraction units."
>
  <!-- SPLIT SCREEN HERO -->
  <div class="split-hero-container">
    <div class="container full-width-split">
      <div class="split-layout">
        <!-- LEFT COLUMN: CONTENT (Hook) -->
        <div class="split-content fade-in-section">
          <span class="service-cat-badge">CARPET & STAIRS • MONTREAL</span>
          <h1 class="split-title fade-in-up text-gradient-empire">
            Carpet Cleaning in Montreal (Homes & Condos)
          </h1>

          <div class="problem-statement fade-in-up delay-100">
            <h3 class="problem-title">Urban Living Challenges:</h3>
            <p class="problem-text">
              In Montreal, city dust, pollen from Mount Royal, and harsh winters (salt, calcium) put your wall-to-wall carpets to the test. These contaminants embed themselves deeply into the fibers of your carpets and stairs.
            </p>
          </div>

          <p class="lead-text fade-in-up delay-200">
            As specialists on the Island of Montreal, we offer steam cleaning by injection-extraction tailored for both houses (via truck-mounts) and high-rise condo towers (via our powerful portable units).
          </p>

          <div class="cta-group fade-in-up delay-300">
            <a href="tel:5148939939" class="btn btn-gradient-green pulse-btn">
              <span class="icon">📞</span> (514) 893-9939 (Montreal Quote)
            </a>
            <button
              onclick="window.openEstimationWidget()"
              class="btn btn-gradient-green"
            >
              <span class="icon">⚡</span> Instant Online Quote
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- RIGHT COLUMN: IMAGE (Visual / Slideshow) -->
        <div class="split-image-wrapper fade-in-section delay-200">
          <div class="slideshow-container">
             <img
              src="/images/catalog/nettoyage-tapis-vapeur-laval.webp"
              alt="Technician cleaning a carpet in a Montreal condo"
              class="slide active"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              fetchpriority="high"
              loading="eager"
            />
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/photo-67.webp"
              alt="Impeccable residential carpet after cleaning in Montreal"
              class="slide"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              loading="lazy"
            />
             <img
              src="/images/catalog/resultat-tapis-propre-longueuil.webp"
              alt="Professional carpet cleaning result"
              class="slide"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="image-overlay-gradient"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-layout">
        <!-- MAIN CONTENT -->
        <div class="service-main">
          <!-- BENEFIT LIST & SEO CONTENT -->
          <div class="fade-in-section delay-100">
            <h2 class="section-title text-gradient-empire">
              Our Montreal Process (Truck-Mount or Portable)
            </h2>

            <p>
              Unlike low-performance rental machines, our professional method guarantees a healthy environment for your family in Montreal:
            </p>

            <ul class="benefit-list" style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
              <li>
                <strong>1. Targeted Pre-treatment:</strong> Application of an enzymatic solution on high-traffic areas to break down oils.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>2. Agitation and Brushing:</strong> Gentle mechanical action to loosen embedded abrasive sand.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>3. Steam Cleaning (Extraction):</strong> Our equipment injects steam and instantly vacuums it up, killing 99% of allergens.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>4. Neutralizing Rinse:</strong> A crucial step to balance the pH. Your carpets will NEVER feel sticky.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>5. Fast Drying:</strong> Thanks to our industrial suction, your carpets generally dry in 3 to 6 hours.
              </li>
            </ul>

            <div style="margin-top: 3rem; background-color: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px;">
               <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                🏢 Experts in High-Rise Condos in Montreal
              </h3>
              <p>
                Do you live on the 15th floor downtown, on Nuns' Island, or in Griffintown? No problem.
              </p>
              <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">
                When our truck-mounts can't reach, we use <strong>professional portable extraction units</strong> (the most powerful in the industry) that deliver comparable results without compromising on quality.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-top: 3rem;">
              <hr class="separator" />
              <h3>A Service Adapted to All Montreal Neighborhoods</h3>
              <p>
                Whether you reside in a duplex in Le Plateau-Mont-Royal, a single-family home in Ahuntsic-Cartierville, or a prestigious residence in Westmount or Outremont, Groupe Nettoyage Empire adapts to your Montreal reality.
              </p>
               <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">
                Regular professional cleaning not only improves the aesthetics of your rooms but also sanitizes the air in your Montreal home against urban pollution and long winter months spent indoors.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- NEW SECTIONS: BENEFITS & FAQ -->
  <section class="section" style="padding-top: 0;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-layout" style="display: block;">
        <div class="service-main" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
           
           <!-- ZONES DESSERVIES -->
          <div class="zones-section" style="margin-top: 3rem; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
            <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.4rem;">Boroughs and Linked Cities — Montreal</h3>
            <p>We serve the entire Island of Montreal with maximum scheduling flexibility:</p>

             <div class="city-group">
              <div class="badges-container">
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Downtown & Old Montreal</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Le Plateau-Mont-Royal</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Westmount & Outremont</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Rosemont–La Petite-Patrie</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Villeray–Saint-Michel–Parc-Extension</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Ahuntsic-Cartierville</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Town of Mount Royal (TMR)</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Saint-Laurent</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 LaSalle & Verdun</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Nuns' Island (Île-des-Sœurs)</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Pierrefonds, Kirkland & West Island</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Mercier–Hochelaga-Maisonneuve</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="contact-footer">Request fast service in Montreal: <strong>(514) 893-9939</strong>.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- FAQ -->
          <div class="fade-in-section delay-300" style="margin-top: 3rem;">
            <h2 class="section-title text-gradient-empire">
              Frequently Asked Questions — Montreal
            </h2>
            <FAQSchema
              faqs={[
                 {
                  question:
                    "Do you clean carpets in Montreal condos (10th floor+) without a balcony?",
                  answer:
                    "Yes, absolutely. We use industrial portable extraction units. They plug into your outlets and use water from your sinks/tubs, allowing us to reach any floor in Montreal without loss of power.",
                },
                {
                  question:
                    "How long does it take for a carpet to dry in a heated apartment during winter?",
                  answer:
                    "Thanks to our strong extraction, the drying time is very fast: generally between 3 and 6 hours, which is ideal for Montreal apartments. Letting air circulate accelerates the process.",
                },
                {
                   question:
                    "Do you clean carpets that have suffered winter calcium (salt) stains?",
                  answer:
                    "Yes, we have specific solutions to dissolve calcium, salt, and minerals embedded in hallway and stair carpets during Montreal winters.",
                },
                {
                  question:
                    "What are your lead times for an appointment in Montreal?",
                  answer:
                    "Since we have several teams crisscrossing the island of Montreal daily, we can often offer an appointment within 2 to 4 days, and sometimes the next day depending on availability.",
                }
              ]}
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<script>
  const slides = document.querySelectorAll(".slide");
  if (slides.length > 0) {
    let currentSlide = 0;
    setInterval(() => {
      slides[currentSlide].classList.remove("active");
      currentSlide = (currentSlide + 1) % slides.length;
      slides[currentSlide].classList.add("active");
    }, 4000);
  }
</script>

<style>
  /* Base styles reused from residentiel pages */
  .split-hero-container { background-color: #fff; padding-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0; overflow: hidden; width: 100vw; }
  .full-width-split { width: 100%; max-width: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
  .split-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 0; align-items: stretch; min-height: 80vh; }
  .split-content { background-color: #ffffff; padding: 100px 4rem 4rem 10%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; position: relative; z-index: 2; }
  .service-cat-badge { text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-accent); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; font-size: 0.85rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .split-title { font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 3.5vw, 4rem); color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 1.1; }
  .city-group { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .badges-container { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; }
  .badge { padding: 0.4rem 0.9rem; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.9rem; border: 1px solid transparent; }
  .badge-blue { background: #e8f4fd; border-color: #c5dff0; }
  .problem-statement { background: #ffffff; border-left: 4px solid #ff4444; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0; margin-bottom: 2rem; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(174, 206, 235, 0.3); }
  .problem-title { font-size: 1rem; color: #cc0000; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 700; }
  .problem-text { font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--color-text-main); font-style: italic; }
  .lead-text { font-size: 1.15rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--color-text-main); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; max-width: 650px; }
  .cta-group { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .cta-group { display: none !important; } }
  .split-image-wrapper { position: relative; height: 100%; min-height: 500px; width: 100%; }
  .slideshow-container { position: relative; width: 100%; height: 100%; overflow: hidden; }
  .slide { position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 1.5s ease-in-out; }
  .slide.active { opacity: 1; }
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .split-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; min-height: auto; }
    .split-content { padding: 3rem 1.5rem; order: 1; }
    .split-image-wrapper { order: 2; height: 400px; min-height: 0; }
    .lead-text { max-width: 100%; }
  }
  .service-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 5rem; }
  .section-title { font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-bottom: 2px solid #eee; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; display: inline-block; }
  .separator { border: 0; height: 1px; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); margin: 1.5rem 0; }
  .benefit-list { margin: 2rem 0; list-style: none; padding: 0; }
  .benefit-list li { margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 1.5rem; position: relative; font-size: 1.05rem; }
  .benefit-list li::before { content: "✓"; color: #d32f2f; position: absolute; left: 0; font-weight: bold; }
  .contact-footer { margin-top: 1.5rem; font-style: italic; color: #666; }
</style>
